snippet.textDisplay:
I will be brutally honest here, this one was the weakest from CSB so far. Murshidabadi, Boga Taleb, Sunidhi Nayak, Arnob, these are some of the most powerful singers on their own right. But even with this ensemble it failed, the song selection was poor, this is simply not their type of music, Another point to consider, vocal parts were muffled. Boga Taleb, Murshidabadi has great range which if you muffle, you take their strenght. 

Wishing to see Joler Gaan, Tanjir Tuhin, Jon Kabir, Oni Hasan, Ershad Zaman in the upcoming season. 🤞🏻❤
